# CentrivaLab final static site

This ZIP contains a scalable static website structure for CentrivaLab.

## Structure
- `index.html` – homepage
- `products.html` – product platform page
- `technology.html` – O-CMF technology page
- `applications.html` – applications page
- `publications.html` – publications placeholder
- `support.html` – support and downloadable placeholders
- `contact.html` – contact page
- `specifications/centrivalab-50-34.html` – detailed technical page
- `docs/` – placeholder files for datasheets/manuals
- `assets/` – CSS and SVG assets

## Notes
- Replace the placeholder files in `docs/` with final PDFs when available.
- The structure is designed so new products can be added without changing the top-level navigation.
- To add a future product, copy the existing specification page and update the content.
